### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/services

### Get status of all services
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get status of specific service
GET {{baseUrl}}/bind

### Start a service
POST {{baseUrl}}/bind/start

### Stop a service
POST {{baseUrl}}/bind/stop

### Restart a service
POST {{baseUrl}}/bind/restart

### Test DHCP service
GET {{baseUrl}}/dhcpd

### Test HTTP service
GET {{baseUrl}}/httpd

### Test invalid service (should return 400)
GET {{baseUrl}}/invalid-service

